java.io.Serializable
public class EditTradeoff
extends NewRationaleElementGUI
implements java.io.Serializable

Edit a tradeoff or co-occurrence. Tradeoffs describe ontology entries (NFRs) that should appear on opposite sides of an argument. Co-occurrences describe ontology entries that should occur together in arguments.
